snippet.title: MegaMan X1 Proto Edition(V1.2 final release)
snippet.description:
This is just a little video I put together to announce the final version
of my hack. Everyone knows it as Protoman 21XX. You can also
find the link to it in this description.

This is for the 1.2.1 version of it:
https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/1780/

http://www.romhacking.net/forum/index.php?topic=15184.0
